# Google Maps Platform key for Street View Static + Static Maps satellite imagery.
# Copy this file to .env.local (gitignored) and paste your key. Restrict the key to your
# Pages domain (HTTP referrers) in the Google Cloud console, and enable the
# "Maps Static API" and "Street View Static API".
# Without a key the app still works — scenic stops fall back to a placeholder plus a
# keyless "Open in Street View" deep-link.
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_KEY=

# --- Supabase (sign-in + cloud ride sync) -----------------------------------------------------
# Set BOTH to enable passwordless email sign-in and syncing saved rides + scan history to a
# rider's account. Find them in your Supabase project: Settings -> API -> Project URL and the
# anon/publishable key. The anon key is safe to ship in client code — access is gated by Row
# Level Security (every row is owner-scoped to auth.uid()).
# Leave BOTH blank to build the app localStorage-only (no sign-in, no cloud) — it still works.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
